runiv 0.0.0.9000
  • Reference

DESCRIPTIONs

Source: R/runiv_stats_descriptions.R
runiv_stats_descriptions.Rd

Get DESCRIPTION files of packages available in an R-universe.

runiv_stats_descriptions(universe)

Arguments

universe

A length one character. User or organization name of the the R-universe owner.

Value

a data.frame.

Author

Valerio Gherardi

Examples

runiv_stats_descriptions("vgherard")
